{"tid":976515,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《星空奇遇記4》可能無了期擱置？繼演員退出後 導演也轉拍《權力遊戲》","createTime":"2019-01-10T12:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T02:04:55.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ea810e531bd0a9d29d8e855748f6bee17de2a6fb","tid":976515,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:33:12.000Z","msg":"去年，派拉蒙影業（Paramount Pictures）宣布正在籌備兩部《星空奇遇記》（Star Trek）的電影。但後來卻有消息傳出兩名主演因片酬問題，可能退出電影拍攝。近日，再有關《 星空奇遇記4 》的壞消息傳出，看來《星空奇遇記》的粉絲要心碎了！<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒Deadline報導，原定負責執導《 星空奇遇記4 》的導演S.J. Clarkson，確定接拍HBO的劇集《權力遊戲》前傳。意味著派拉蒙影業應該是擱置了《 星空奇遇記4 》的製作，S.J. Clarkson才有空檔接拍其他作品。<br />\n<br />\n其實，早在上年8月，已有消息傳出飾演卻克艦長的基斯派恩（Chris Pine）和演其父親的基斯咸士禾夫（Chris Hemsworth）因片酬問題，可能退出電影的拍攝。再加上這次的消息，可說是對《星空奇遇記》粉絲的雙重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n雖然《 星空奇遇記4 》可能無法面世，但派拉蒙影業早前宣布在籌備的另一部限制級《星空奇遇記》，已經落實由《復仇勇者》(The Revenant)編劇Mark L. Smith執筆，並由昆頓塔倫天奴（Quentin Tarantino）執導，相信電影仍在製作階段。"},{"pid":"18f6b78123f99507eb63d8e08fc49fe73f434817","tid":976515,"uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"限制級星空奇遇記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694865aef7ce4d8816ca219280138f94ff5be125","tid":976515,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T12:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e220413597383e774ea6cf488db4673951f4b2a6","tid":976515,"uid":19667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"Qt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"h